Return your final response within \boxed{}. Find all triples of pairwise distinct real numbers \( x, y, z \) that are the solutions of the following system of equations:

\[
\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
x^{2}+y^{2}=-x+3y+z \\
y^{2}+z^{2}=x+3y-z \\
z^{2}+x^{2}=2x+2y-z
\end{array}
\right.
\]
